name: Jennifer Bartels
bio: Human. Actor. Writer. Lover of any version of Creep. Addicted to Insulin. Horrible Sleeper. Lover of Self work. Always learning ❤️

social_posts.post_text: My Xmas/NYE and the fun and very cold memories around that time. Not “cold memories” like no one hugged each other, it was just very cold outside. I will always wish California was next to North Carolina. #family #xmas

Happy birthday to @brotography_dude Thanks for that walk with Duffy. Cheers to a great year filled with cold noodle salads, late night songwriting, long hikes holding my snacks and new adventures. Thank you for being you John. #birthday

It is super fun to meet and work with such talented and kind people and play, all while eating chips. @chadjamian I am very thankful to know you and you are a gem. @chevonnehughes_official you are kind and funny and same. @ryanradis as well, great funny grade A people. A great group directed by @coultergirl ( thanks for letting us play and feel safe to try whatever) thanks to @rmbcasting as always and @cesdtalent #tostitos #chips #stressreliefsnacks

Love these fun and informative @northropgrumman spots. I truly love pizza and good people and learning about science and tech and… pizza again. Thanks @lesleywolffisthephotobomb and @cesdtalent and @abshirethedirector and the pals I have made from the start.
Happy Mother’s Day to my sweet @mamabartels I love you and miss you so much. Thanks for being my best friend.

Happy Father’s Day to all the amazing dads out there. Very thankful for my Dad, his energy and jokes and guidance, and his ever changing beard styles. Love you and miss you everyday from the west coast. Shout out to my sweet Uncle Ed, who has always been like a dad to me as well. And love to my Uncle Rico. Miss you everyday!
We surprised my family in #raleigh for a July 4th gift. We then created a very patriotic explosion that channeled the 4th grade @brotography_dude

@brotography_dude you are my best friend and partner and you are currently running to get me juice due to a blood sugar low in Mexico at a sick resort as we celebrate a great couple and our own love. Happy one year anniversary. You make me laugh so much. And you make me feel so safe and supported and truly like I’m awesome just the way I am. Thank you for loving me and dealing with me when Jenny and the Sleepmores sing “5 more minutes.” Thank you for holding my hand through things. Thank you for sharing your family and your friends and embracing mine. A year ago, this was unexpected, but I think that is what life is about. Current blood sugar 62. Hope this makes sense. I love you @brotography_dude Love, Cubica, Pet, Your lil little tangerine. #anniversary #love

My sweet BNS @juststoppinby I hope you have the best birthday and you like the pictures I posted (after all the threats leading up to this said post.) I love you and am both inspired and proud of you my little nugget. Have the best day and year to come and never forget when you used to steal my clothes and pinch my skin with your little chard nails and Eddie and I had to form an allegiance for safety after you threw a phone. #birthday #birthdaygirl #sisters #love
Minus the vertigo and haunting doubt and fears of all my karmic mistakes coming for retribution on that space needle, I had a good time. #seattle #spaceneedle

Wow. July was a whirlwind and a huge highlight was the amazing wedding celebrating @thetrailtohealth and @adamholcomb2 in Valle de Guadalupe, Mexico. Amazing company, new friends and Delicious nibbles amongst a backdrop that took my breath away. Very thankful for Adam and Erika and cheers to their new chapter. Love to my partner in crime @brotography_dude and my buddies @mexitoosh @nathanstreifel @cliffleebehangin @ldg_la for making this vacation and wedding extra memorable. You really can by anything at a bodega! #mexico #wedding #valledeguadalupe #elencuentro

An epic weekend with stops for @cinequestorg in #sanjose and #sanfrancisco treats and #Sonoma fun. Love and adore my pals @thesammorgan @_jackiequinones_ and supporting our indie film @closetedpeoplepleaser in these weird times. I loved NORCAL and am super thankful. @brotography_dude you are my best friend and one of the funniest guys in the world. Thanks for driving me over the bridges and letting me listen to classic 60’s tailored to  the San Fran region. #indie #sanfrancisco #treats #t1d #sanjose #cinequest

This is 42. This has been one of the most special birthday weeks. (I scaled back from the standard birthday month), but it was jam packed and beautiful nonetheless. Thankful for the birthday wishes, little goodies, backyard parties, amazing trips and the love. I really felt it. And sometimes feeling that love is the most important thing to keep you circling the sun another year, pancreas or not. Cheers to more giggles and wishes coming true, and brow lamination and baby Botox. #morrobay #madonnainn #birthday #type1 #snacks #winery #otters #mirrors #smiling
